OL,6,FWatch the moment that the portrait of
OL,7,FKing Charles is unveiled
OL,9,FA new portrait of King Charles has
OL,10,Fbeen unveiled at Windsor Castle.
OL,12,FIt is the first official portrait of
OL,13,FCharleson May 6 last year.
OL,15,F"It is remarkable actually how it has
OL,16,Fturned out," Charles commented after
OL,17,Fthe portrait was unveiled.
