OL,3,CFirst official portrait of King
OL,4,CCharles unveiled
OL,6,FThe painting is by artist Jonathan
OL,7,FYeo, who was commissioned to create
OL,8,Fthe piece in 2020 to celebrate the
OL,9,Fthen Prince of Wales' 50 years as a
OL,10,Fmember of The Drapers' Company in 2022.
OL,12,FThe company was founded more than 600
OL,13,Fyears ago as a group of woollen cloth
OL,14,Ftraders but has since evolved into a
OL,15,Fgrant-giving body.
OL,17,FCharles is shown in the portrait to be
OL,18,Fwearing the uniform of the Welsh
OL,19,FGuards, of which he was made
OL,20,Fregimental colonel in 1975.
