OL,4,CCharles unveiled
OL,6,FMr Yeo had a total of four sittings
OL,7,Fwith the monarch between June 2021 and
OL,8,FNovember 2023 in order to complete the
OL,9,Fpainting, and in between sessions
OL,10,Fworked from drawings and photos he had
OL,11,Ftaken of the King.
OL,13,FThe artist said it had been a
OL,14,F"privilege and pleasure" to be
OL,15,Fcommissioned to do the painting.
