OL,3,CFirst official portrait of King
OL,4,CCharles unveiled
OL,6,FMr Yeo is known for his "distinctive"
OL,7,Fstyle, according to his website.
OL,9,F"He employs a range of media and
OL,10,Ftechniques to create a diverse body of
OL,11,Fwork that expands the traditional
OL,12,Fparameters of portraiture," Dr
OL,13,FNicholas Cullinan, Director of the
OL,14,FNational Portrait Gallery, said in
OL,15,F2016.
OL,17,FThe canvas size - approximately 8.5 by
OL,18,F6.5ft framed - was designed to fit
OL,19,Fwithin the architecture of Drapers'
OL,20,FHall and the context of the paintings
OL,21,Fit will eventually hang alongside.
