OL,6,FOther people painted by Jonathan Yeo
OL,7,Finclude actors Nicole Kidman and Idris
OL,8,FElba, artist Damien Hearst and former
OL,9,Fprime ministers Tony Blair and David
OL,10,FCameron.
OL,12,FHe has also painted the late Prince
OL,13,FPhilip and Queen Camilla.
OL,15,FIn 2018 Yeo was named artist of the
OL,16,Fyear by GQ Magazine and he is
OL,17,Fcurrently artist Trustee of the
OL,18,FNational Portrait Gallery.
